{"tid":1508540,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［集體智慧］圍狗時只攻前方? 我覺得突擊先係高招","createTime":"2019-08-26T14:21:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T14:51:44.000Z","uid":61690,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"aeb7e768657601b0bd67ee959eeb2985b4d12e89","tid":1508540,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:21:51.000Z","msg":"睇返琴晚荃灣段片:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_wOthnnB7eM?t=58\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_wOthnnB7eM%3Ft%3D58&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsZmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=166541c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_wOthnnB7eM?t=58</a><br />\n當然明白事出突然, 大家無咁多時間諗咁多。不過事後檢討可以避免下次犯錯<br />\n<br />\n大部份人企位都係只係係正前方，<span style=\"color: red;\">後排手足只係塞住左（如果有返咁上下既人）</span><br />\n你見popo都只係守住前面，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">佢地無理過格離／後面，咁樣佢地好危險</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gLXtHUi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgLXtHUi.png&h=e8844401&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果下次類似場面出現有d<span style=\"color: red;\">伏擊兵（綠色），拉闊個對抗範圍</span>，popo多幾面要睇要守，佢地肯定會淆。<br />\n伏擊兵係進退都得，情況許可可以暗地進擊，衝出黎飛踢一件落地。假設唔許可既話，果邊無乜人，逃走都快Ｄ。整個觀感上係圍住砌，士氣大增。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yzzsd4X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyzzsd4X.png&h=681e6aa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n戴返個頭盔先，呢個圍砌戰略前題係黑衫人數係popo人數3倍以上，同埋<span style=\"color: red;\">黑衫佔上風果時用</span>，勢色唔對既話，走為上計。<br />\n<br />\n集體智慧，大家覺得岩唔岩用？岩用既幫手推下post，歡迎提出意見。"},{"pid":"bf713dc24b380c8cf400893f62d1fd8256395ec6","tid":1508540,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:22:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最新post 睇得清楚d + 加左明天有義士再審係頂！</span></span>(極正經)(請推至長期置頂)被捕義士進程，一個也不能少不只是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5a45b0cea99114cdc696bb7019bf6a7f99beadb1","tid":1508540,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:22:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"71b1adaa07ef69a77e1c7c545b836c17da41c40a","tid":1508540,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:24:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5b7fb24ba26a8af2ee88730a43b1808ea229374f","tid":1508540,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:25:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bbeed551fbba016a1a1e83ffdd17d6fa034090e9","tid":1508540,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:26:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f24abe385bf79279b594cff26c957375dd36426a","tid":1508540,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:27:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ce9698dfad231b0991026cd391715cde8ace9c43","tid":1508540,"uid":190858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:28:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">[核彈文宣]828#ProtestToo集會全世界都要去 平權=反極權 將火源燒開去</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1508048/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1508048/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qBGBRCw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqBGBRCw.jpg&h=c9bbcd64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d02b9c59b74f34e0a0a0829a7c241a5f85ccf62","tid":1508540,"uid":42740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:28:47.000Z","msg":"反包圍講左好耐<br />\n別動隊好需要勇氣 而且無人LEAD住好困難"},{"pid":"ec228a4e71e78b5991f6ce0244e595b4c0aa6c39","tid":1508540,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:28:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a hre